@node Calculator

Calculator : (File guis:tools/calc.gc)
--------------------------------------

This is a full calculator with a ticker tape etc, which uses ARexx
to calculate the result. Click on the RMB and the window will open
up and provide you with a ticker tape display. Click on any line
in the listview, and the main calc window will be updated with the
value on that line.

This GUI is actually an independent gui and can be operated by itself 
if needed, or attached to any other guis you make.

@endnode
