@node PPShow

PPShow : (file dir/dir.ppshow)
------------------------------

Hit the PPShow button and you'll get a gui which will play 
all selected picture/anim files in order, with the settings
you have given in the gui.

You MUST have the PPShow program (by Nico Francois) in your c: dir.

Although this gui is only for the PPShow viewer, with a little
tampering of the script file you can change it for any other player
you prefer. The options (Speed, resolution etc) will be similar,
so the changes will be few. 

@endnode
